title: By the Queene. The Queenes Maiesties proclamation, declaring her princelie intention to inhibit her subiects vpon most extreme paines, from offending on the seas any persons in their ships or goods, being the subiectes of any prince, potentate, or state, in amitie with her Maiestie.
author: England and Wales. Sovereign (1558-1603 : Elizabeth I)
